### Appendix C: Messaging Guardrails\
\
\uc0\u9989  **Do**:\
- Lead with pain, not aspiration\
- Use DJ-specific lexicon (EPK, Circuit, A1/A2)\
- Show, don't tell: embed UI screenshots in copy\
- Anchor price to gig value, not tool cost\
- Make testimonials verifiable and metric-backed\
\
\uc0\u10060  **Don't**:\
- Claim "only" or "best" without proof\
- Repeat the same benefit 4+ times without deepening\
- Show development/staging URLs in screenshots\
- Offer competing CTAs in the hero section\
- Leave advanced features vague or unexplained\
